 Mexico War]\n* [http://www.vmi.edu/archives.aspx?id=4294968301 Robert E. Lee Mexican War Maps in the VMI Archives]\n* [http://www.history.vt.edu/MxAmWar/INDEX.HTM ''The Mexican War and the Media, 1845\u20131848'']\n* [https://www.loc.gov/rr/program/bib/ourdocs/Guadalupe.html Treaty of Guadalupe Hidalgo and related resources at the U.S. Library of Congress]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070403114842/http://www.familytales.org/results.php?tla=wfs Letters of Winfield Scott including official reports from the front sent to the Secretary of War]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20061027184404/http://www.usa-presidents.info/pierce/mexican-war.html Franklin Pierce's Journal on the March from Vera Cruz]\n* [http://mexicanhistory.org/MexicanAmericanWarTimeline.htm Mexican\u2013American War Time line]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20130120021520/http://www.civilwaranimated.com/MexicoAnimation.html Animated History of the Mexican\u2013American War]\n* [http://omniatlas.com/maps/northamerica/18460513/ Maps showing course of Mexican-American War at omniatlas.com]\n\n===Other===\n* [https://www.pbs.org/kera/usmexicanwar PBS site of US-Mexican war program]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110202172504/http://battleofmonterrey.com/ Battle of Monterrey Web Site] \u2013 Complete Info on the battle\n* [https://www.pbs.org/kera/usmexicanwar/educators/md3_war.html Manifest Destiny and the U.S.-Mexican War: Then and Now]\n* [http://www.lnstar.com/mall/texasinfo/mexicow.htm ''The Mexican War'']\n* [http://www.smithsonianeducation.org/educators/lesson_plans/borders/start.html Smithsonian teaching aids for \"Establishing Borders: The Expansion of the United States, 1846\u201348\"]\n* [http://www.dmwv.org/mexwar/history/concise.htm A History by the Descendants of Mexican War Veterans]\n* [http://histclo.com/country/us/hist/19/ush-mexw.html Mexican\u2013American War]\n* [http://www.latinamericanstudies.org/mex-war/Blacks-Mexican-War.pdf Invisible Men: Blacks and the U.S. Army in the Me