441\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u041c\u0430\u043a\u0441\u0438\u043c\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447 \u041b\u043e\u0433\u0430\u0448\u043e\u0432}}; born 20 August 1991) is a [[Russia]]n professional [[Association football|football]]er who plays for [[FC Rostov]].\n\n==Club career==\nHe made his professional debut in the [[Russian First Division]] in 2008 for [[FC Sportakademklub Moscow]].<ref name=career>{{FootballFacts.ru|21608<!-- -logashov-arsenij-maksimovich -->}}</ref>\n\nOn 3 February 2017, he moved to [[FC Tosno]], signing a contract until the end of the 2016\u201317 season.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Tosno]]|url=http://fctosno.ru/news.php?readmore=2503|script-title=ru:\u0410\u0420\u0421\u0415\u041d\u0418\u0419 \u041b\u041e\u0413\u0410\u0428\u041e\u0412 - \u0412 \u00ab\u0422\u041e\u0421\u041d\u041e\u00bb \u0414\u041e \u041a\u041e\u041d\u0426\u0410 \u0421\u0415\u0417\u041e\u041d\u0410|date=3 February 2017|language=Russian|access-date=4 February 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204170701/http://fctosno.ru/news.php?readmore=2503|archive-date=4 February 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\nOn 11 June 2017, he signed a 2-year contract with [[FC Baltika Kaliningrad]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Baltika Kaliningrad]]|url=http://www.fc-baltika.ru/news/nash-klub-podpisal-kontrakt-s-eshhe-odnim-novichkom|script-title=ru:\u041d\u0430\u0448 \u043a\u043b\u0443\u0431 \u043f\u043e\u0434\u043f\u0438\u0441\u0430\u043b \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043a\u0442 \u0441 \u0435\u0449\u0435 \u043e\u0434\u043d\u0438\u043c \u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447\u043a\u043e\u043c|date=11 June 2017|language=Russian}}</ref>\n\nOn 20 June 2018, he returned to [[FC Rostov]], signing a 3-year contract.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[FC Rostov]]|url=http://www.fc-rostov.ru/press/news/11731|script-title=ru:\u0410\u0440\u0441\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u041b\u043e\u0433\u0430\u0448\u043e\u0432 \u0432\u0435\u0440\u043d\u0443\u043b\u0441\u044f \u0432 \u00ab\u0420\u043e\u0441\u0442\u043e\u0432\u00